{"tid":645914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支爆唔到跟本香港人都有份","createTime":"2018-04-28T14:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T07:40:15.000Z","uid":116572,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dbaf6d5ced301022cd02f620e1400f3c7368f4fa","tid":645914,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"中國平安(2318)分拆旗下業務平安健康醫療科技(1833)上市，於4月23日至26日公開招股，5月4日掛牌上市。<br />\n<br />\n平安好醫生雖然有「獨角獸」和「互聯網醫療健康」概念，但是過去三年，<strong>公司都是以億計地蝕錢，而且一年蝕得比一年多，<span style=\"color: red;\">2015年純利蝕人民幣3.23億，2016年蝕7.58億，2017年蝕10億 </span> </strong>，更是累進地蝕錢！<br />\n<br />\n越蝕越多又點，結果？<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，平安好醫生 獲超購逾658倍，涉及22萬人認購 ，凍資約3760億<br />\n<br />\n遲啲小米又上市抽水(好似話想以1000億美金估值來港上市)，到時個個香港股民又爭住送錢上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.capital-hk.com/wealth-management/expert-tips/jia-zhi-jie-ma-fa-ping-hao-yi-sheng-shang-shi-hou-zou-shi-hui-si-yi \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.capital-hk.com%2Fwealth-management%2Fexpert-tips%2Fjia-zhi-jie-ma-fa-ping-hao-yi-sheng-shang-shi-hou-zou-shi-hui-si-yi%20&d=RAoqGISUx%2BsfqzXPWYbO3f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=8ae0de29\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.capital-hk.com/wealth-management/expert-tips/jia-zhi-jie-ma-fa-ping-hao-yi-sheng-shang-shi-hou-zou-shi-hui-si-yi </a>"},{"pid":"9e655e838b69e257ac6073b4424915e25768cea8","tid":645914,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"真係爆時，就一齊攪掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a2452f4e24406c4291615f7024aa6750b9abc6","tid":645914,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蝕錢公司都有港豬輸血"}]}